<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Notebook Entry</div>
<dl id="n05018c"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n05" href="#n05018c">N05 (VI.B.2)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n05all.htm#n05018c"> 18(c)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> work the <font color="green">[deck]</font> / cast lots</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">Jonah went <mark>on deck and the crew cast lots</mark> to see who was the cause of all the trouble. Properly they cast &ldquo;the stone&rdquo; by which the lot was determined. Casting lots was common even among the Jews. <small> G.W. Foote, <a name="BROM" href="../../ff/fdra/fdex.htm#BROM"><cite title="source">Bible Romances</cite></a>, 4th ed. (1922) [Jonah and the Whale] 140</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
